Titolo: Earn to Die 2

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Earn to Die 2 is a game developed by Russian indie studio Toffee Games, which is the sequel to 2012's Earn to Die. Earn to Die 2 sees a departure from the familiar desert setting of the original game, and delves into the depths of cities overrun by zombies. Players have to get through the city in order to reach checkpoints and the finish to win the game level.